```
class Solution {
public:
    int bitwiseComplement(int n) {
        return n>0? (int)((1ll<<((int)log2(n)+1))-1)^n : 1;
    }
};

```
ANALYSIS:-
* **Time Complexity :-** BigO(logN)

* **Space Complexity :-** BigO(1)

